Effects of liraglutide on depressive behavior in a mouse depression model 
and cognition in the probe trial of Morris water maze test 
Mi Kyoung Seo a, Sehoon Jeong a,b,c, Dae-Hyun Seog d,e,f, Jung An Lee g, Jae-Hon Lee h, 
Yena Lee i, Roger S. McIntyre j,k, Sung Woo Park a,f,*, Jung Goo Lee a,g,* 
